        <updateDate>2011-02-28T22:59:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Recovering Missing Children Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow the disclosure of tax returns and return information to officers and employees of state or local law enforcement agencies&nbsp;who are partnering with a federal agency in&nbsp;investigations of missing or exploited child cases and who are personally and directly engaged in such investigations.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
